        <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Started with a Vision. Built Through Experience.</h2>

        <p>
          Obvius Digital was founded by Tolu Mebaanne and Kayla Sippel — two Seneca Digital Marketing graduates with a combined decade of experience between media production, publishing, and communications. We started this agency because we saw the same gap over and over: small businesses with something real to offer, struggling to communicate it in a way that matched their actual value.
        </p>

        <p>
          Our first client came through a capstone project. Since then, we've been growing steadily through our academic and professional networks — working with businesses who want more than a vendor. They want someone who shows up, learns their brand, and builds work that reflects who they actually are.
        </p>

        <p>
          We're a home-based startup with agency-level output. Our size is our advantage: it keeps us lean, communicative, and genuinely invested in every project we take on.
        </p>
